---
layout: layouts/blog.njk
title: Aktualności
description: W naszym publicznym zakładzie opieki zdrowotnej zawsze staramy się być na bieżąco z najnowszymi trendami w dziedzinie opieki zdrowotnej i terapii.
pagination: 
    data: collections.posts
    size: 8
    alias: blog
---

  <div class="row gx-4">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h1 class="xl" data-splitting>
        {{ title }}
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <div class="row gx-4 pt-small">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="row gx-5"> 
        {% for post in collections.posts.slice(0,3) %}
        <div class="col-md-6 fadeIn pb-small">
            <div class="post-card">
                <p class="color-accent-1 mb-2">
                    <small>
                       {{ post.data.date | dateDisplay}}
                    </small>
                </p>
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" title="{{ post.data.title }}">
                    <h2 class="archive-post-title h5 mt-3 mb-3">
                        {{ post.data.title }}
                    </h2>
                </a>
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" title="Czytaj" class="link-arrow mt-3 mb-4">
                    Czytaj
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M13 1L1 13" stroke="var(--color-dark-1)" stroke-width="1"
                            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                        <path d="M3 1H13V11" stroke="var(--color-dark-1)" stroke-width="1"
                            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
      <div class="row gx-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <nav>
            <ul class="pagination d-flex fadeIn"> {%- for pageEntry in pagination.pages %} <li class="pagination-item">
                <a class="pagination-link" href="{{ pagination.hrefs[ loop.index0 ] }}" {% if page.url == pagination.hrefs[ loop.index0 ] %} aria-current="active" {% endif %}>{{ loop.index }}</a>
              </li> {%- endfor %} </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>